Marguerite Whitten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marguerite_Whitten 0 Marguerite Whitten (February 23, 1913, Greenville, Mississippi – December 25, 1990, Los Angeles County, California) was an American film actress appearing in 14 films between 1938 and 1943, often with actor Mantan Moreland.
